- "Faded into the background" metaphorically means "deprecated";
- "Gathering dust in the corridors of time" implies the signals have not been updated or used recently;
- "Guardianship of the ancient one" refers to being owned by the user with ID 1;
- "Memory in the annals of the system" hints at the signals being past records in the database;
